              [btev_c0.gif] How to join the BTeV Collaboration
     __________________________________________________________________

   All new members must be favorably reviewed by the membership committee
   and approved by a body widely representative of the collaboration
   (initially the executive committee) and by the full collaboration.
   Click here for the full membership procedure.

   Contact Jeff Appel -- chairman of the membership committee --
   appel@fnal.gov

   or Joel Butler (butler@fnal.gov) or Sheldon Stone
   (stone@suhep.phy.syr.edu).
